reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Issues with the drawer alignment
reviews.reviewText: We got two of these night stands and one went together flawlessly. The other has a serious alignment issue with one of the drawers. The assembly was easy enough and everything went together like it was supposed to with the exception of the top drawer of one of them. It juts out over the edge it’s designated space so it can’t close fully.We triple checked to be sure that we didn’t put a piece on upside down or anything, but it appears to be a matter of some holes being drilled in the wrong place. It’s annoying, but not a deal breaker since it’s in a corner out of sight from casual view.The actual tables are really sturdy and look good. I hate to judge the product based on what was probably just a piece that slipped through quality control when the overall product is so solid and honestly really nice for the relatively low price point, but I figure it should be noted for anyone on the fence about buying them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Misalignment of drawers
reviews.reviewText: I like this side table. Nice and Sturdy. Went thru the directions, put it all together and the top drawer wouldn't close all the way. The bottom drawer was too short. The bottom box that holds the drawers doesn't specify top or bottom. So, we unscrewed the bottom box, rotated it and tested the drawers and they closed completely. So... if you find this to be your problem, the bottom box is most likely installed upside-down. The drawer glides will work either way so no need to remove them. Hope this helps someone.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Small but Good quality
reviews.reviewText: I must say this cabinet is smaller than I expected, and it doesn't hold much. But the quality is better than I expected, and the wood is thick and strong. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Arrived well-packaged and with good instructions. Be prepared to take your time with assembling. I am pretty good at putting things together but needed a power screwdriver to get some of the screws fully screwed in. The drawers do not open as smoothly as I would like but, for the price, I think this is a good product.
